   "source": [
    "# Synthetic 3D T1 Brain Tumor MRI (NIfTI Latent Diffusion)\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook trains an unconditional 3D latent diffusion model for synthetic T1 brain tumor MRI volumes directly from NIfTI data."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "161433c3",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Workflow (NIfTI 3D, Unconditional T1 Generation)\n",
    "1. Discover 3D T1 `.nii`/`.nii.gz` files recursively.\n",
    "2. Train a 3D `AutoencoderKL` on T1 volumes.\n",
    "3. Freeze the autoencoder and train a latent DDPM UNet.\n",
    "4. Use EMA UNet for stable sampling and decode synthetic T1 volumes.\n",
    "5. Save generated volumes as NIfTI with optional reference affine/header."
   ]
  },
